Feature: Logging Dice
  
  Login into Dice and search for jobs

  @login
  Scenario Outline: Logging in Dice                           # Dice.feature:6
    Given Runmode is "<Runmode>"
    Given I go to "loginURL" on "<Browser>"
    And I enter "search-field-keyword" as "<JobTitle>"
    And I enter "search-field-location" as "<SearchLocation>"
    And I click on FindJobs  "FindJob"
    When I click on JobsPage "JobsPage2"
    Then I click on contract checkbox "contract_checkbox"
    Then I click on contractw checkbox "contractWCheckbox"
    Then I click on links_on_page "links_on_page4"

    Examples: 

  @login
  Scenario Outline: Logging in Dice                             # Dice.feature:21
    Given Runmode is "Y"                                        # Dice.runmode_is(String)
    Given I go to "loginURL" on "Mozilla"                       # Dice.i_go_to_on(String,String)
    And I enter "search-field-keyword" as "Selenium Automation" # Dice.i_enter_as(String,String)
    And I enter "search-field-location" as "Dallas,TX"          # Dice.i_enter_as(String,String)
    And I click on FindJobs  "FindJob"                          # Dice.i_click_on_FindJobs(String)
    When I click on JobsPage "JobsPage2"                        # Dice.i_click_on1(String)
    Then I click on contract checkbox "contract_checkbox"       # Dice.i_click_on_contract_checkbox(String)
    Then I click on contractw checkbox "contractWCheckbox"      # Dice.i_click_on_contractw_checkbox(String)
    Then I click on links_on_page "links_on_page4"              # Dice.i_click_on_links_on_page(String)

